      • s_fTraceLogging

        public static boolean s_fTraceLogging
        The executor attribute to indicate whether trace logging is enabled.

        By default, the executor trace logging is disabled. logging can be enabled by either setting the coherence.executor.trace.logging system property or the TraceLogging attribute on the JMX ExecutorMBean or via Management over REST.
